('about_bizs', '<p><strong><span style="font-size:medium;"><span style="font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'';">一、团旮旯的团购价格和数量</span></span></strong></p><blockquote style="margin: 0 0 0 40px; border: none; padding: 0px;"><p><span style="font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'';"><strong>1</strong>. 团旮旯有权对团购产品的团购券价格进行修改。</span></p><p><span style="font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'';"><strong>2</strong>. 团旮旯有权对团购产品的每人最高限购数，及团购产品的总数量进行限制与修改。</span></p><p><span style="font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'';"><strong>3</strong>. 团旮旯有权设置团购项目的排序方式。</span></p><p><span style="font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'';"><strong>4</strong>. 商户组建团购时，即视为认可团购以上各项。</span></p></blockquote><p><strong><span style="font-size:medium;"><span style="font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'';">二、商户须知</span></span></strong></p><blockquote style="margin: 0 0 0 40px; border: none; padding: 0px;"><p><span style="font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'';"><strong>1</strong>. 商户有权免费发布不违反法律法规的任意商品团购信息，商户可自定制团购内容项下的各类服务。</span></p><p><span style="font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'';"><strong>2</strong>. 如买家有需求，商户需向买家开具足额正式发票，特殊表明的除外，团旮旯不负责亦无义务向买家开具发票。足额指消费者的团购券购买金额或现场消费的实际金额，而非团购项目或服务的原价格。</span></p><p><span style="font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'';"><strong>3</strong>. 为保障买家获得有品质的服务，商户应保证在团购项目建立时尽可能详尽的描述项目，并在项目有变更的时候尽量事先通知。未提前说明或事先通知的，团旮旯不承担任何责任。</span></p><p><span style="font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'';"><strong>4</strong>. 买家使用旮旯卷在商户消费过程中产生的体验感受、服务品质等均由商户负责，团旮旯对此不作任何承诺。</span></p><p><span style="font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'';"><strong>5</strong>. 商户应对其产品对买家在直接消费过程中可能产生的所有伤害及损害（包括无法确认旮旯券而造成购买者无法使用）、疾病等负完全责任。买家在消费过程中的所有伤害及损害均与团旮旯无关。</span></p></blockquote><strong><span style="font-size:medium;"><span style="font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'';">三、详细细则</span></span></strong><br /><blockquote style="margin: 0 0 0 40px; border: none; padding: 0px;"><p><span style="font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'';"><span style="font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; "></span></span></p><p><span style="font-family: ''Microsoft YaHei''; "><strong>商户合作细则及合作方式请详细咨询<a href="http://www.tuangala.com/about/contact.php" target="_blank">团旮旯客服</a></strong>。</span></p></blockquote>'),
('about_terms', '<span style="font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; line-height: 18px; "><h3 style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; outline-width: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-color: initial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; ">一、产品价格与数量</h3></span><ul class="infoList" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 18px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; outline-width: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-color: initial; list-style-type: none; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); "><li style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; outline-width: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-color: initial; ">1. 团旮旯有权对团购产品的团购券价格自主定价。</li><li style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; outline-width: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-color: initial; ">2. 团旮旯有权对团购产品的每人最高限购数，及团购产品的总数量进行限制与修改。</li><li style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; outline-width: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-color: initial; ">3. 买家购买团购产品，视为认可团购价格、限购数量，并接受旮旯卷券及网页上的商家说明所提示的使用限制、本协议条款及其它相关规则。</li></ul><h3 style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; outline-width: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-color: initial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; ">二、团旮旯团购券（以下简称"旮旯券"）</h3><ul class="infoList" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 18px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; outline-width: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-color: initial; list-style-type: none; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); "><li style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; outline-width: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-color: initial; ">1. 旮旯券是用户成功购买团购产品后，通过手机短信或打印获取，仅作为持有旮旯券的用户（本协议简称"买家"）去商户的消费凭证，不可兑换现金。</li><li style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; outline-width: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-color: initial; ">2. 一般情况下，旮旯券不可与商户其他优惠同时享用，除非商户允许或特别说明。</li><li style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; outline-width: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-color: initial; ">3. 旮旯券必须在有效期内使用，超过有效期的团购券不可作为消费凭证，除下述第4条明确规定者外，不可申请退款。</li><li style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; outline-width: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-color: initial; ">4. 旮旯券不记名、不挂失，如因买家个人保管不善等原因导致的遗失、泄漏密码、或造成冒领等，由买家本人负责。</li></ul><h3 style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; outline-width: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-color: initial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; ">三、买家须知</h3><ul class="infoList" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 18px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; outline-width: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-color: initial; list-style-type: none; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); "><li style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; outline-width: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-color: initial; ">1. 买家有权获得旮旯券所明示内容项下的各类服务，除旮旯券规定不直接予以兑换的情形外，买家有权凭旮旯券至商户处消费并获得服务。</li><li style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; outline-width: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-color: initial; ">2. 买家持旮旯券进行消费后，有权要求商户向用户开具足额正式发票，团旮旯不负责亦无义务向买家开具发票。足额指消费者的旮旯券购买金额或现场消费的实际金额，而非团购产品或服务的原价格。</li><li style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; outline-width: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-color: initial; ">3. 为保障买家获得有品质的服务，买家应按照旮旯券的要求进行消费，并尽量事先进行预约后消费。旮旯券规定必须事先预约的，买家应提前预约，未提前预约的，团旮旯不承担任何责任。</li><li style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; outline-width: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-color: initial; ">4. 买家使用旮旯券在商户消费过程中产生的体验感受、服务品质等均由商户负责，团旮旯对此不作任何承诺。</li><li style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; outline-width: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-color: initial; ">5. 商户应对其产品对买家在直接消费过程中可能产生的所有伤害及损害（包括无法确认旮旯券而造成购买者无法使用）、疾病等负完全责任。买家在消费过程中的所有伤害及损害均与团旮旯无关。</li><li style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; outline-width: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-color: initial; ">6. 买家应从旮旯卷指定的位置直接购买团购产品。如从任何其它第三方渠道购买获得的旮旯券，因此发生的任何问题，如不能获得产品或服务等，团旮旯概不负责。</li><li style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; outline-width: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-color: initial; ">7. 买家在购买旮旯卷券后，通过任何其它第三方平台自行交易、转让的，如发生该券失效等问题，团旮旯不承担任何责任。</li></ul><h3 style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; outline-width: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-color: initial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; ">四、退款规则</h3><ul class="infoList" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 18px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; outline-width: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-color: initial; list-style-type: none; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); "><li style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; outline-width: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-color: initial; ">消费者在发生以下情况时，我们随时安排退款，如遇其他情况消费者可拨打<a href="http://www.tuangala.com/about/contact.php" target="_blank">客服电话 或发邮件</a>，我们将秉持尊重消费者的原则，个案处理。</li><li style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; outline-width: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-color: initial; ">1. 未达到最小团购人数，造成当次团购未成功的。</li><li style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; outline-width: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-color: initial; ">2. 买家团购款项实际已支付，但购买当次团购产品未成功的。</li><li style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; outline-width: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-color: initial; ">3. 买家团购成功后，因商户原因不能在团购有效期内提供服务或拒绝提供服务的。</li><li style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; outline-width: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-color: initial; ">4. 买家在团旮旯帐号中未消费的剩余金额部分可退款。</li></ul><h3 style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-right-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; outline-width: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-color: initial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; ">五、具体细则可咨询<a href="http://www.tuangala.com/about/contact.php">团旮旯客服</a></h3>'),
