('about_job', '<h3><div style="background-color: rgb(192, 192, 192);font-size:medium;" width="100%">推广助理(全国) </div></h3><p><span style="font-size:x-small;"><span style="font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'';"><strong>工作职责</strong>：</span></span></p><blockquote style="margin: 0 0 0 40px; border: none; padding: 0px;"><p></p><span style="font-family: ''Microsoft YaHei'';font-size:x-small; ">1. 协助完成市场部推广计划；</span><br /><span style="font-family: ''Microsoft YaHei'';font-size:x-small; ">2. 策划新的推广方式；</span><br /><span style="font-family: ''Microsoft YaHei'';font-size:x-small; ">3. 执行临时性推广任务；</span><br /><span style="font-family: ''Microsoft YaHei'';font-size:x-small; ">4. 与各位推广渠道进行沟通；</span><p></p></blockquote><p><span style="font-size:x-small;"><span style="font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'';"><strong>职位要求</strong>：</span></span></p><blockquote style="margin: 0 0 0 40px; border: none; padding: 0px;"><p></p><span style="font-family: ''Microsoft YaHei'';font-size:x-small; ">1. 专业不限；</span><br /><span style="font-family: ''Microsoft YaHei'';font-size:x-small; ">2. 有过成功的组织活动经验(线上，线下均可)；</span><br /><span style="font-family: ''Microsoft YaHei'';font-size:x-small; ">3. 有过成功的推广经验(线上，线下均可)；</span><br /><span style="font-family: ''Microsoft YaHei'';font-size:x-small; ">4. 乐于接受挑战，具有开拓意识；</span><br /><span style="font-family: ''Microsoft YaHei'';font-size:x-small; ">5. 对团购有深入的理解；</span><p></p></blockquote><p><span style="font-size:x-small;"><span style="font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'';">有兴趣？请发送一封标题格式为"</span></span><span style="font-weight: bold;"><span style="font-size:x-small;"><span style="font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'';"><span style="color:#33CC00;">推广助理-姓名-工作城市</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:x-small;"><span style="font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'';">"的邮件到 </span></span><span style="font-size:x-small;"><span style="font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'';"><span style="color:#33FF33;"><strong>admin@hhdem.com</strong></span></span></span><span style="font-size:x-small;"><span style="font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'';">。</span></span></p>'),
('help_bizhowtouse', '<h2><span style="font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'';">1. 商户成功注册 </span><span style="font-size:x-small;"><a href="http://www.tuangala.com/parnter/create.php"><span style="font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'';">立刻注册</span></a></span></h2><h2><span style="font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'';">2. 商户后台菜单功能说明如下：</span></h2><blockquote style="margin: 0 0 0 40px; border: none; padding: 0px;"><p><span style="font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'';">1) 首页 : 列出本商户建立的所有团购项目列表</span></p><p><span style="font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'';">2) 建立团购 : 新建团购功能, 每个商户最多只能建3个活动中的团购项目</span></p><p><span style="font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'';">3) 商户资料 : 商户资料的修改</span></p><p><span style="font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'';">4) 旮旯卷列表 : 商户建立的团购项目产生的旮旯卷</span></p></blockquote><h2><span style="font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'';">3. 买家在商户的消费</span></h2><blockquote style="margin: 0 0 0 40px; border: none; padding: 0px;"><p><span style="font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'';">1) 买家到商户处消费时, 商户可通过商户后台或团旮旯首页右上角的''旮旯卷验证及消费登记''功能查询旮旯卷有效性</span></p></blockquote><blockquote style="margin: 0 0 0 40px; border: none; padding: 0px;"><p><span style="font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'';">2) 买家持旮旯卷消费后, 商户可通过商户后台或团旮旯首页右上角的''旮旯卷验证及消费登记''链接登记旮旯卷消费情况</span></p></blockquote><h2><span style="font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'';">4. 商户与团旮旯团购站的结算</span></h2><blockquote style="margin: 0 0 0 40px; border: none; padding: 0px;"><p><span style="font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'';">1) 每月底至下月4日之前是结算日, 结算本月产生的消费费用</span></p><p><span style="font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'';">2) 单次结算费用需大于等于200元</span></p><p><span style="font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'';">3) 其他情况需特殊说明的, 解释权归团旮旯所有</span></p></blockquote>');

