yle="word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(254, 36, 25); font-size: 14px; "><span style="word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(92, 88, 90); font-size: 14px; ">二、体检中<br style="word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; " />9、到达体检中心后，请您先到前台登记，认真填写“个人健康信息表”中各项内容，并将您目前身体的不适和曾患疾病告知医生，以利于健康分析和评估。<br style="word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; " />10、下列检查项目须空腹完成：采血、腹部B超、隐血珠、碳十三呼吸试验、电子胃/肠镜检查、腹部CT检查。内科检查前请您先测血压。<br style="word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; " />11、已怀孕和准备怀孕的女性请先告知医护人员，我们将不安排您做放射科检查。婴幼儿和少年儿童不安排X线放射检查。<br style="word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; " />12、胸透等X线检查前，请您出去并妥善保管金、银、玉器等饰物。<br style="word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; " />13、女性客人做盆腔B超检查前1小时，请到餐饮区饮水6-8杯（400-500ml），以保证盆腔超声的准确。<br style="word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; " /><br style="word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; " />三、体检后<br style="word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; " />14、个人《体检报告》将电话通知您前来领取；团体《体检报告》将封存后如期返回您的单位。<br style="word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; " />15、请您认真听取医生的建议，及时复查、随诊或治疗。<br style="word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; " />16、如果您对体检结果有疑问或有其他身体不适，欢迎致电咨询（电话详见体检报告首页）。</span></span></span></span></span></p><p style="word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; padding-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 5px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; "><span style="word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(254, 36, 25); font-size: 14px; "><span style="word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(92, 88, 90); font-size: 14px; "><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); "><span style="word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(254, 36, 25); font-size: 14px; "><span style="word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(92, 88, 90); font-size: 14px; "><br /></span></span></span></span></span></p><p style="word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; paddi