n-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; list-style-type: none; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; "><span style="font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'';color:#FFFFFF;"><strong><img src="http://www.tuangala.com/static/team/2010/1125/12906594769133.jpg" alt="" /><br /></strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; list-style-type: none; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; "><span style="font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'';">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; list-style-type: none; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; "><strong><span style="font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'';"><span style="color:#ffffff;background-color: rgb(102, 204, 0); "></span></span></strong><span style="font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'';">&nbsp;</span></p><h1>&nbsp;了解欧洲第一背包品牌-Deuter &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</h1><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; list-style-type: none; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; "><strong><span style="font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'';">拥有百年历史的欧洲顶级品牌</span></strong></p><ul style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; list-style-type: none; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; "><li style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 1.7em; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; list-style-type: disc; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; "><span style="font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'';">德国Deuter公司是欧洲最著名的背包生产及设计商。它创建于1898年，距今已有100多年的历史。它是全球休闲运动用品行业中居于领先地位的大型跨国企业，业务范围遍及全球三十三个国家和地区。&nbsp;<br />Deuter公司拥有一批忠实的客户。他们的建议、批评和期许造就了今天的Deuter：一个努力靠近用户并寻找最好的途径以达成目标的品牌。</span></li><li style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 1.7em; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; list-style-type: disc; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; "><span style="font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'';">更多品牌介绍参见517户外网户外装备的Deuter专页：</span><a href="http://www.517huwai.com/brand/10" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(51, 153, 153); text-decoration: none; "><span style="font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'';">http://www.517huwai.com/brand/10</span></a><span style="font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'';">&nbsp;</span></li><li style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 1.7em; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; list-style-type: disc; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; "><span style="font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'';">Deuter中国官方网站：</span><a href="http://www.deuter.cn/" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(51, 153, 153); text-decoration: none; "><span style="font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'';">http://www.deuter.cn/</span></a></li></ul><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; list-style-type: none; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; "><span style="font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'';"><strong></strong>&nbsp;</span></p><h1>多项开创性技术</h1><ul style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; list-style-type: none; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; "><li style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 1.7em; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; list-style-type: disc; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; "><span style="font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'';">1984年Deuter以Tauern为主体，并引用通风式背负系统的概念，开发出全世界第一个三面透气系统网架透气系统；</span></li><li style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 1.7em; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; list-style-type: disc; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; "><span style="font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'';">1988年 推出第一个网架透气系统背包，因为它具降低25﹪排汗量的功能，使的背负者更舒适轻松，至今销售超过50万个可见其魅力，也因此成为所有透气式背包所争相仿效的对象；</span></li><li style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 1.7em; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; list-style-type: disc; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; "><span style="font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'';">1996年因为登山健行、雪地旅游活动时，让背负重心贴近身体重心是很重要的。因此，又设计出更好的背负系统---拔热透气系统；</span></li><li style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 1.7em; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; list-style-type: disc; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; "><span style="font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'';">1998年推出更高等级网架透气系统，网架背包的使用人数持续快速成长。</span></li></ul><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; list-style-type: none; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; "><span style="font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'';">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; list-style-type: none; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; "></p><h1>载誉满满</h1><span style="font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'';">20